'''貝德福德'''（{{lang-en|Bedford}}）是[[英國|英國]][[貝德福德郡|貝德福德郡]]的[[郡治|郡治]]，位於[[東英格蘭|東英格蘭]]。它是更大的[[貝德福德區|貝德福德區]]的行政中心，與[[肯普斯頓|肯普斯頓]]、[[埃爾斯托|埃爾斯托]]和[[拜登漢姆|拜登漢姆]]聯合形成人口106,940的都會區。<ref name="BUA">{{cite web | url=http://www.nomisweb.co.uk/articles/747.aspx | title=2011 Census - Built-up areas | work= | publisher=[[Office_for_National_Statistics|ONS]] | accessdate=2013-08-09 | archive-date=2013-09-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921045319/http://www.nomisweb.co.uk/articles/747.aspx | dead-url=no }}</ref>

==歷史==
{{See also|貝德福德郡歷史}}

貝德福德之名來自於一個名叫貝德（Beda）的[[撒克遜|撒克遜]]首領，<ref>{{cite web | publisher=Bedford Borough Council | url=http://www.bedford.gov.uk/leisure_and_culture/local_history_and_heritage/brief_history_of_bedford.aspx | title=Brief History of Bedford | accessdate=2011-03-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208003952/http://www.bedford.gov.uk/leisure_and_culture/local_history_and_heritage/brief_history_of_bedford.aspx | archive-date=2015-12-08 | dead-url=yes }}</ref> ford指的則是[[大烏茲河|大烏茲河]]邊的[[淺灘|淺灘]]。[[盎格魯-撒克遜|盎格魯-撒克遜]]國王[[奧法_(麥西亞)|奧法]]在796年埋葬於此地。<ref name=BEASE_133>Simon Keynes, "Cynethryth", in Lapidge, ''Encyclopaedia of Anglo-Saxon England'', p. 133.</ref> 886年成為分隔[[丹麥區|丹麥區]]和[[威塞克斯王國|威塞克斯王國]]的邊境鎮。<ref>{{cite web | publisher=Bedfordshire Libraries | url=http://www.galaxy.bedfordshire.gov.uk/webingres/bedfordshire/vlib/0.digitised_resources/bedford_digitisation_timeline_early.htm | title=Bedford Timeline, Earliest Times – 1800 | accessdate=2008-02-10 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081201083747/http://www.galaxy.bedfordshire.gov.uk/webingres/bedfordshire/vlib/0.digitised_resources/bedford_digitisation_timeline_early.htm | archivedate=2008-12-01 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book
 | last = Whitelock
 | first = Dorothy
 | coauthors = Douglas, David C. (ed)
 | title = ''English Historical Documents c. 500–1042'' (2nd edition)
 | publisher = Routledge
 | year = 1979
 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=EUSqIR2qaaIC&pg=PA416&dq=bedford+886+danes&sig=JmxDJNcfoi60LftEpzKr097ZxuA
 | accessdate = 2008-02-10
 | archive-date = 2016-12-23
 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161223205054/https://books.google.com/books?id=EUSqIR2qaaIC&pg=PA416&dq=bedford+886+danes&sig=JmxDJNcfoi60LftEpzKr097ZxuA
 | dead-url = no
 }}</ref> 屬於[[貝德福德男爵領地|貝德福德男爵領地]]的中心。919年[[長者愛德華|長者愛德華]]在烏茲河南岸建起了這裡第一座已知的堡壘，後來這座堡壘被丹麥人摧毀。[[威廉二世_(英格蘭)|威廉二世]]建議貝德福德男爵重新建造一座堡壘，但是新的[[貝德福德城堡|貝德福德城堡]]也在1224年被夷平，如今僅存一堆廢墟。<ref>{{cite web | publisher=CastleUK | url=http://www.castleuk.net/castle_lists_midlands/153/bedfordcastle.htm | title=Bedford Castle | accessdate=2008-02-10 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080305044532/http://www.castleuk.net/castle_lists_midlands/153/bedfordcastle.htm | archivedate=2008-03-05 | deadurl=no }}</ref>

1166年，[[亨利二世_(英格蘭)|亨利二世]]授予貝德福德皇家憲章。<ref>{{cite web | publisher=Bedford Borough Council | url=http://www.bedford.gov.uk/Default.aspx/Web/BriefHistoryofBedford | title=Brief History of Bedford | accessdate=2008-02-10 | archive-date=2011-07-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716141901/http://www.bedford.gov.uk/Default.aspx/Web/BriefHistoryofBedford | dead-url=no }}</ref> [[中世紀|中世紀]]的貝德福德一直是個農業鎮，16世紀之後貝德福德和貝德福德郡成爲了英格蘭蕾絲製造業中心，[[貝德福德郡蕾絲|貝德福德郡蕾絲]]直到20世紀初還是當地的重要產業。

1552年，區內第一間私立學校[[Bedford_School|Bedford School]]成立。

1660年，[[約翰·班揚|約翰·班揚]]囚禁于[[貝德福德監獄|貝德福德監獄]]中，他在這裡一呆就是12年。并於此地寫成了《[[天路歷程|天路歷程]]》。<ref>{{cite web | publisher=The Bunyan Press | url=http://www.bunyanpress.co.uk/jbunyan.htm | title=John Bunyan (1628–1688) | accessdate=2008-02-10 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070726053136/http://www.bunyanpress.co.uk/jbunyan.htm | archivedate=2007-07-26 }}</ref>

19世紀貝德福德開始轉型成為工業城市，1832年引入瓦斯照明，1846年接入鐵路。第一家穀物交易所建造于1849年，<ref>{{cite web | publisher=Bedford Corn Exchange | url=http://www.bedfordcornexchange.co.uk/ | title=1849 & Friday 1 March 1850 | accessdate=2008-02-10 | archive-date=2021-05-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210508222930/https://www.bedfordcornexchange.co.uk/ | dead-url=no }}</ref> 第一條排水道在1864年始建。<ref>{{cite web | publisher=Bedfordshire County Council | url=http://www.bedfordshire.gov.uk/CommunityAndLiving/ArchivesAndRecordOffice/GuidesToCollections/BedfordBoroughRecordsIntroduction.aspx | title=Bedford Borough records introduction | accessdate=2008-02-10 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080827174804/http://www.bedfordshire.gov.uk/CommunityAndLiving/ArchivesAndRecordOffice/GuidesToCollections/BedfordBoroughRecordsIntroduction.aspx | archivedate=2008-08-27 }}</ref>

